Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.95,0:00:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.99,0:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使受了傷也無妨  不轉移目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想熱切、激烈地生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.99,0:00:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我永不放棄的堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.99,0:00:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想緊緊抱著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.99,0:00:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去或痛楚都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.99,0:01:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引導至鮮明的、一瞬間的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸中的鼓勵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.99,0:01:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你延續而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回歸財團的特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就任世界國家的元首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.14,0:01:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功再次統一了地面的軍備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主張衛星獨立的白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.58,0:01:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了巨大宇宙戰艦天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.52,0:01:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令官米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威脅要肅清地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始和特列斯\N率領的世界國家軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆發全面戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.92,0:01:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈駕駛員們不隸屬任何陣營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類史上最慘烈的\N戰鬥即將展開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.28,0:02:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會白費她帶來的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特在天秤座裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.36,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希爾妲好像在天秤座內見過她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十六話\N[米利亞爾特的決心]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到巨大戰艦天秤座攻擊的地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.74,0:03:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正準備以壓倒性的軍力作出反擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數千機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.48,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以宇宙用里歐為主要軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.05,0:03:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集結在最接近地球的資源衛星MO_II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.89,0:03:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯表明會親自出征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.99,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令士兵們戰意高昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但機動戰士部隊能和巨大戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對抗到哪地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.53,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱有疑問有意見也並非沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.31,0:03:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.65,0:03:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前線指揮始終太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.22,0:03:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特也在前線作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.55,0:04:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把今次出擊作為對他的禮節吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我好好記著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.73,0:04:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉禮節的戰爭只會產生殺戮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.80,0:04:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前在地球發生的戰爭是可悲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.49,0:04:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技師長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.49,0:04:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是被棄在上盧森堡的機體吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這是出色的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人去了宇宙之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把火箭裝在這種東西上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒意義吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可半途而廢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球上已經沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能駕駛這種機體的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛究竟去了哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.09,0:05:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他乘坐回收的比爾哥輸送艇出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的地不問也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他拋下零式走了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.13,0:05:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想徒手和傑克斯對抗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.24,0:05:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何方法也好，那傢伙會做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.14,0:05:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我認為他的目的不只那樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你說他去救那位小姐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我對那傢伙評價太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.48,0:05:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為他是這裡最正常的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位小姐擁有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推動希洛那種男人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.43,0:05:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛，希洛帶莉莉娜回來後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你至少和她打聲招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女性比你更易受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.17,0:05:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，如果要追那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點去比較好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不可減低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬年和平號的防衛力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且也不用妨礙他們兩人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真是信任希洛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.62,0:06:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那傢伙也會失手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.97,0:06:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第202萬年和平號攻擊部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.27,0:06:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推進動力部和左舷中彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在要進入緊急甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是天秤座艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確定生還者，說出識別編號…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒有生還者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.49,0:06:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  等等 停船  喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.90,0:07:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心\N駕駛的可能是破壞間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火勢撲滅了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.18,0:07:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在滅火啊\N我們也已盡了力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.18,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!封鎖這區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不準任何人離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給敵人潛進來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!又不小心了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.93,0:07:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該曾多次叫你們加緊戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.57,0:07:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜點我早料到會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.54,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，比我想像中快得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特大人，怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他既然來了，我只好前去見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但還未確定潛入來的人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.62,0:07:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是他，希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒話和王兄以外的人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們別再管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果妳在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.52,0:08:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵他們就會猶豫不決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒想過你會來!希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!我還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.76,0:08:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯嗎? 就讓妳見他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有事找他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,座標修正完畢，目標天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫希爾妲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女孩帶來的戰艦的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在有幫助了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在看來不在艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王兄的所在?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能的地方只有幾處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是一個不可思議的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還不及妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.20,0:09:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，你賜予我生存的力量和希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對其他人也一定是那樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.34,0:09:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別要我重覆多次，我還不及妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.05,0:09:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，找到傑克斯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為我和妳已經談完了
