Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們等米利亞爾特大人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這樣下去…
