Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就不會知道戰鬥的愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.98,0:13:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要讓全人類知道那一點
