Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是繼承爸爸的遺志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.91,0:13:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是父王的遺志?
